<i>Kandi is forever</i>
<i>grateful for Bertha's wise</i>

14:14.253 --> 14:16.121
<i>"tell it like it is" advice.</i>

14:16.188 --> 14:18.224
<i>So now Kandi</i>
<i>is giving Bertha's old house</i>

14:18.290 --> 14:21.594
<i>the renovation it</i>
<i>truly deserves.</i>

