<i>In the front patio,</i>

15:37.403 --> 15:40.039
<i>I have my guys replacing</i>
<i>all the old windows, which will</i>

15:40.105 --> 15:44.310
<i>give Aunt Bertha better</i>
<i>insulation and an updated look.</i>

